snippet.title: High Heat Baseball 2004 (PS2) - Intro
snippet.description: The opening movie for High Heat Baseball 2004 (released in 2003) for the PlayStation 2, by the 3DO Company. Starring Curt Schilling in his Arizona Diamondbacks days.
